---
title: Quick Chicken and Apricot Tagine with Turmeric Roasted Cauliflower and Couscous
description: Our chef Mimi is a bit of a cauliflower fanatic and in her opinion there’s no better way to cook this cloud shaped veg than roasting! “It’s so pretty when it’s all golden from the oven with the turmeric,” she says. She’s totally right, give this dish a go and it’ll be a vibrant feast for your eyes and for your taste buds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-turkey-and-apricot-tagine-7eb85338.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/quick-turkey-and-apricot-tagine-875296b5.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/quick-turkey-and-apricot-tagine-30-57500563fd2cb95b1f8b4567
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Middle Eastern
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
